        <abstract>
            <p>Consoling to CD that JC gives "a little more age to the world".</p> 
<p>Cites article by Henry Moseley ["On the mechanical possibility of the descent of glaciers", <hi rend="italic">Proc. R. Soc. Lond.</hi> 17 (1869): 202–8].</p> 
            <p>Mentions article by A. R. Clarke on shape of the globe.</p>
